 padding-left: 18px; font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><li style=""><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Médico Clínico Geral</span></p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style=""><font color="#0f1115" style="font-weight: 600;">Médico da Saúde da Família</font><u style=""><font color="#2563eb" style=""> <b>COM RQE</b></font></u></p></li><li style="margin-top: 6px;"><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph" style=""><font color="#0f1115" style="font-weight: 600;">Médico Pediatra </font><font color="#2563eb" style=""><b><u>COM RQE</u></b></font></p></li></ol></div><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><ul style="margin-top: 16px; padding-left: 18px; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Segoe UI&quot;, Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, &quot;Open Sans&quot;, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); margin-bottom: 0px !important;"><li><p class="ds-markdown-paragraph"><span style="font-weight: 600;">Regime de Trabalho:</span>&nbsp;Os profissionais devem estar disponíveis em regime de&nbsp;<span style="font-weight: 600;">plantão de 24 horas por dia, 7 dias por semana</span>, de forma ininterrupta.</p></li></ul><p></p></div><p><br></p><p><font color="#dc2626"><b></b></font></p><div data-highlight-box="true" style="background-color: rgb(240, 253, 244); border: 2px solid rgb(34, 197, 94); border-radius: 6px; padding: 12px; margin: 8px 0px; display: block; min-width: 100px;"><p><font color="#dc2626"><b>PONTO CRITICO: A